<item>
            <title>[LU-12944] Migration corrupts xattrs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12944</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When migrating files and directories from one MDT to another, if they happen to have xattrs set, then their values will be corrupted once migration is complete.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;More precisely, the size used to store the xattr value on the migrated file/dir is taken from previous xattrs set, so it might be wrong.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
